data.description:
This 4 bedroom 2 bath home is nestled on a gorgeous piece of property that is approximately 4 acres. You will find beautiful views of the lake from your living room and one of the upstairs  master suits.  Not only does this home  offer TWO master suites,  an updated kitchen, but it is equipped with an adorable  guest house that has GREAT rental potential. 
 This is a must see.
